sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant tRPC
    participant Validator
    participant DB

    Client->>tRPC: object.create(data)
    tRPC->>Validator: Validate with Zod
    alt Validation fails
        Validator-->>Client: TRPCError (BAD_REQUEST)
    else Validation passes
        Validator->>DB: Insert object
        DB-->>tRPC: Created object
        tRPC-->>Client: Object with metadata
    end
